---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="2025 — The New Horizons Challenge"
  description="The 2025 New Horizons Challenge — relay run from the Sun to Pluto on October 11, 2025."
>

  <nav slot="subnav" class="hidden md:block sticky top-14 z-40 theme-nav border-b py-2">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4">
      <ul class="flex justify-center gap-1">
        <li><a href="/new_horizons" class="nav-link">&larr; New Horizons</a></li>
        <li><a href="#relay"        class="nav-link">Relay Legs</a></li>
        <li><a href="#logistics"    class="nav-link">Logistics</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ── Header ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="theme-section-alt py-12 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">2025 Challenge</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500">October 11, 2025 &mdash; Madison, WI</p>
      <p class="text-green-600 font-bold text-lg mt-2">WE DID IT!</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Relay Legs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="relay" class="theme-section py-16 px-4 [scroll-margin-top:110px]">
    <div class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-10">Relay Legs</h2>

      <div class="max-w-md mx-auto">
        <div class="divide-y divide-gray-100 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          {[
            { leg: 'Sun to Mars',       dist: '1 Mile',    athletes: 'Owen, Liang Liang, Stephen', time: '8-80 Minutes' },
            { leg: 'Mars to Saturn',    dist: '4 Miles',   athletes: 'Partic and Tim',             time: '32 Minutes' },
            { leg: 'Saturn to Uranus',  dist: '4 Miles',   athletes: 'Taylor, Maddy, Max',         time: '32 Minutes' },
            { leg: 'Uranus to Neptune', dist: '>5 Miles',  athletes: 'Maddy and Max',              time: '48 Minutes' },
            { leg: 'Neptune to Pluto',  dist: '9.75 Miles',athletes: 'Brady and Alan J',           time: '70 Minutes' },
          ].map(({ leg, dist, athletes, time }) => (
            <div class="py-4 px-5 text-center">
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">{leg}</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Distance: {dist}</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Athletes: {athletes}</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Estimated Time: {time}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Spotify -->
      <div class="mt-12 max-w-md mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4 text-center">Need Music?</h3>
        <iframe
          style="border-radius:12px"
          src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/3qLG1XdspF6Pd37BjTeV0Z?utm_source=generator"
          width="100%"
          height="352"
          frameborder="0"
          allowfullscreen
          allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
          loading="lazy"
        ></iframe>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Logistics ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="logistics" class="theme-section-alt py-16 px-4 [scroll-margin-top:110px]">
    <div class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-10">Logistics</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">

        <!-- Date / Weather -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">Date and Time</h3>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">7.30a on Saturday, 10.11.2025 at the Dovecote</p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Last year, the relay took 3 hours and 15 minutes. Brix Cider opens at 11a on Saturdays
            so we can start anytime after 7.45a. We will start around 8a in case anyone decides to
            be a hero and run way faster than expected.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            If you are not at the Dovecote by the time we need to leave for your leg, we will have
            to leave without you (which would be a bummer). If you won't be able to make it to the
            Dovecote around 7.30a, let Stephen know and he can get an estimate for the time by which
            you would need to make it.
          </p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">Weather Policy</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
            We will play this by ear. A little rain never hurt anyone, but a lot of rain and/or
            lightning have hurt people. Cross your fingers that we don't have to postpone.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Getting there -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">Getting to Your Relay Leg</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The plan is to drive folks from location to location. To be most efficient, homebase
            will be the Dovecote. Please find your own way here.
          </p>
          <div class="divide-y divide-gray-100 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
            {[
              {
                heading: 'Stephen drops a car near Mars with Mars',
                details: [
                  'Sun walks to Sun (Monona Terrace)',
                  'Mars leaves from Mars and Stephen takes car back to the Dovecote',
                  'Liang Liang probably just meets us at Mars for the walk to Sun',
                ],
              },
              {
                heading: 'Taylor drives to Odana Hills GC and drops Saturn off',
                details: [
                  'Saturn walks to Saturn (take a right down the bike path)',
                  'Mars walks back to car and Mars returns to the Dovecote with car',
                ],
              },
              {
                heading: 'Stephen drives to Goose Lake and picks Taylor up',
                details: [
                  'Uranus continues from Saturn (Double leg for Max and Maddy)',
                  'Saturn walks back to car and Stephen returns to the Dovecote',
                ],
              },
              {
                heading: 'Al drives to Epic near Stable and drops a car and Neptune off',
                details: [
                  'Neptune walks to Neptune (take ramp down to bike path and take a right)',
                  "Uranus walks back to car and Max drives Al's car to Brix with Uranus",
                ],
              },
              {
                heading: 'Stephen and spectators drive to Brix Cider',
                details: ['If anyone wants to come for the celebration at Brix Cider, they are more than welcome to join us!'],
              },
            ].map(({ heading, details }) => (
              <div class="py-4 px-5">
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">{heading}</p>
                {details.map(d => <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">{d}</p>)}
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="theme-section py-8 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto text-center text-gray-500 font-medium">
      Questions? Please reach out to Stephen.
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
